  <bioghist id="aspace_020c72e5c6935679ea10f5f84c9349f8">
    <head>Biographical / Historical</head>
<p>Corazon Aquino succeeded Ferdinand Marcos as president of the Philippines in 1986.</p>  </bioghist>
  <scopecontent id="aspace_cf2b45f89e6e9575d7c6885792f4c51c">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Clippings from Philippine and United States newspapers, together with 3 magazine articles. Newspapers include the New York times, Philippine star, People's journal, Philippine daily inquirer, Manila evening post, Los Angeles times, and others.</p>  </scopecontent>
